headline: KIT KAT® Brand Debuts First-Ever Seasonal Shape: KIT KAT® Santas
summary: Santa Claus deserves a break, and thanks to KIT KAT®, he's getting one this year with the launch of its first-ever seasonal shape - KIT KAT® Santas! Available for a limited time only, this new KIT KAT® treat is a festive addition to the brand's product lineup that is adorned with imprinted boots, a jolly smile and an even crispier wafer-to-chocolate ratio than a traditional KIT KAT® bar.
